          "settings": {
            "text": "Toi et Moi Promise Rings",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_WrWViD": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A Toi et Moi promise ring is one of the most meaningful ways to represent a shared connection between two people. Translating from French as “you and me”, the design features two stones set side by side, symbolising two individuals brought together in a single moment of commitment.<br/><br/>At The Promise Co, this idea aligns perfectly with what a promise ring is meant to represent. Each Toi et Moi promise ring captures the balance between two people, two stories and two lives coming together, while still remaining individual.<br/><br/>Our collection reimagines this timeless design through modern, wearable styles. Whether you choose matching stones, contrasting shapes or a more minimal interpretation, every ring reflects the idea that a promise is not about losing individuality, but about strengthening it together.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_UNLxbx",
        "richtext_WrWViD"
